                <h4 class="my-4">Gifted Artworks</h4>
                <p>The museum also exhibits a collection of gifted artworks from Satya Bhama Jalan of Patna, Bihar, further enriching its diverse array of exhibits.</p>
                <h3 class="my-3">Visitor Experience</h3>
                <p>The Bhagalpur Museum remains open to the public and is a popular destination for locals and tourists alike. It is known for its well-curated exhibits and engaging tours, which bring the region's history and culture to life. The museum is wheelchair accessible, ensuring a comfortable visit for all guests.</p>
